{"word":"ἰνδάλλομαι","slug":"ἰνδάλλομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<entryFree id=\"n50501\" key=\"i)nda/llomai\" type=\"main\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"entryFree\"> <orth extent=\"full\" lang=\"greek\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"orth\">ἰνδάλλομαι</orth>, almost always used in <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ pres.\">pres.</a></tns> and <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ impf.\">impf.</a></tns>: <tns opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tns\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ aor.\">aor.</a></tns> <sense id=\"n50501.0\" n=\"A\" level=\"1\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἰνδάλθην</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lyc.\">Lyc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">597</biblScope></bibl></cit>,<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">961</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1487.tlg001:163\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Max.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">163</biblScope> </bibl>:—<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">appear, seem</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἄλλοι μοι δοκέουσι παροίτεροι ἔμμεναι ἵπποι, ἄλλος δ᾽ ἡνίοχος ἰνδάλλεται</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:23:460\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">23.460</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἰνδάλλετο δέ σφισι πᾶσι τεύχεσι λαμπόμενος μεγαθύμου Πηλεΐωνος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:17:213\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">17.213</biblScope> </bibl> </cit> (<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">-θύμῳ -ωνι</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Aristarch.</author></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg1767.tlg001:2\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2</biblScope> </bibl>), cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:3:246\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.246</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0013.tlg005.perseus-grc1:178\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">h.Ven.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">178</biblScope> </bibl>: <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ὥς μοι ἰνδάλλεται ἦτορ</foreign> as my memory <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">seems</tr_> to me, or perh., as my heart <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">pictures him</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:19:224\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">19.224</biblScope> </bibl>; also in <gramGrp opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gramGrp\"> <gram type=\"dialect\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"gram\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Att.\">Att.</a></gram></gramGrp>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ὥστ᾽ ἔμοιγ᾽ ἰνδάλλεται ὁμοιότατος κλητῆρος εἶναι πωλίῳ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg004.perseus-grc1:188\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ V.\">V.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">188</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">τοῦτο γάρ μοι ἰ. διανοουμένη [ἡ ψυχή], οὐκ ἄλλο τι ἢ διαλέγεσθαι</foreign> it <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">seems</tr_> to me to be merely engaged in a dialogue, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg006.perseus-grc1:189e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Tht.\">Tht.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">189e</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τὰ δι᾽ ὀφθαλμῶν ἰνδαλλόμενα ἡμῖν</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0086.tlg028:397b:18\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Arist.\">Arist.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Mu.\">Mu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">397b18</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. lamb.<bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\">Myst.</title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.3</biblScope> </bibl>; <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">flash on one's mind</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἀμφὶ δὲ . . μεληδόνες ἰνδάλλοντο</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">appeared</tr_>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:3:812\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ A.R.\">A.R.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">3.812</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0001.tlg001.perseus-grc1:2:545\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.545</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"2\" id=\"n50501.1\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> c. dat., <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">resemble</tr_>, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">θεοὶ ξένοις -όμενοι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg030.perseus-grc1:381e\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ R.\">R.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">381e</biblScope></bibl></cit>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:959a\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">959a</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ἀργύρῳ</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0005.tlg001.perseus-grc1:22:39\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Theoc.\">Theoc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">22.39</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">κύκνοις</quote_> <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lyc.\">Lyc.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">597</biblScope></bibl></cit>. (Never in Trag.; connected with <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">vid-</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Εἴδω</foreign>.)</sense> </entryFree>"}]}